            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>上月我們報道過， Apple 推出了「Final Cut Pro for iPad 2」（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/08/final-cut-pro-and-logic-pro-2024/software/ipad-app/">相關報道</a>），最矚目的相信是「Live Multicam」功能，同一時間最多數可連接 4 部攝影機之餘，更可同時預覽 4 部攝影機拍攝畫面。今天小編就和大家分享一下，如何使用「Final Cut Pro for iPad 2」 連接多部 iPhone 拍攝。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246511" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09747-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09747-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09747.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>Step 1 下載並訂閲 Final Cut Pro for iPad</h2><p>要使用這個功能，首先你需要下載並訂閲「Final Cut Pro for iPad 2」。Final Cut Pro for iPad 需要付費訂閲，小編的 iPad 已經訂閲了，未訂閲的朋友需要先訂閲才能使用。如果你本身有安裝 Final Cut Pro for iPad 的話，要看看是否已經更新至 2.0 版本。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246342" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo1719395842-694x482.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo1719395842-694x482.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo1719395842.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲下載 ／ 更新 Final Cut Pro for iPad 2.0 版本</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246372" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/1-11-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/1-11-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/1-11.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊左下角的「+ new project」</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246423" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo1719399914-694x482.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo1719399914-694x482.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo1719399914.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊「Continue」</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246425" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo1719399979-694x482.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo1719399979-694x482.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo1719399979.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊「Live Multicam」</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246425" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo1719399979-694x482.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo1719399979-694x482.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo1719399979.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊「Live Multicam」</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246431" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo1719401155-694x482.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo1719401155-694x482.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo1719401155.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊「Continue」</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246432" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo17194011551-694x482.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo17194011551-694x482.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo17194011551.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲繼續點擊「Continue」</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246433" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo17194011552-694x482.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo17194011552-694x482.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo17194011552.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊「允許」</p><h2>Step 2 在 iPhone 下載 Final Cut Camera</h2><p>此時要拿出你的 iPhone，安裝 Final Cut Camera。請注意，要安裝 Final Cut Camera， 需要更新 iOS 至 17.4 或以上版本。</p><p>Final Cut Camera 下載連結：<a href="https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/final-cut-camera/id6469552837">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/final-cut-camera/id6469552837</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246434" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo1719401945-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo1719401945-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo1719401945.jpeg 369w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲下載 Final Cut Camera</p><p>開啟 Final Cut Camera 後，會看見下圖的畫面，點擊「Continue」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246435" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo1719401932-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo1719401932-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo1719401932.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊「Continue」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246436" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo17194019321-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo17194019321-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo17194019321.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲繼續點擊「Continue」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246437" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo17194019322-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo17194019322-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo17194019322.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊「允許」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246439" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2-11-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2-11-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2-11.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊左上角綠色框框住的按鍵</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246440" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo17194019325-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo17194019325-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo17194019325.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊「Continue」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246441" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo17194019326-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo17194019326-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo17194019326.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊「允許」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246443" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo17194019327-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo17194019327-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo17194019327.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊「允許」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246446" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/3-7-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/3-7-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/3-7.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲選擇安裝有 Final Cut Pro 的 iPad</p><p class="preface">下圖是 iPhone 開啟 Final Cut Camera 時螢幕顯示的畫面。使用 iPhone 相機拍攝的影像會即時在 Final Cut Pro for iPad 上顯示，雖然有大約半秒延遲，但對實際使用並無太大影響。</p><p class="preface"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246448" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo17194019329-694x320.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="320" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo17194019329-694x320.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo17194019329.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲iPhone 拍攝時的畫面</p><p>連接多個裝置後， iPad 顯示畫面如下：</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246642" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo1719483362-694x482.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo1719483362-694x482.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/photo1719483362.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可以在 iPad 上同時看見多個裝置拍攝的畫面</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246648" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09751-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09751-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09751.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲實際拍攝畫面如上</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1246651" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09761-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09761-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09761.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/14/apple-vision-pro-preorder-2/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】Apple Vision Pro 香港預訂教學　戴眼鏡也能輕鬆買 + 臉部掃描過程</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/30/iphone-circle-to-search-by-shortcut/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】iPhone 也可「畫圈搜尋」　輕觸機背即可使用 + 即影即 Google</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/01/apple-starts-work-on-ios-19-and-macos-16/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">《彭博》指 Apple 已經著手開發，明年推出 iOS、macOS、watchOS 的新版本</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2> </h2><h2>總結：簡單易用輕鬆連接　延遲率低</h2><p>雖然 Multicam 並不是甚麼新鮮功能，但 Final Cut Pro for iPad 連接非常便捷，而且延遲率非常低，小編體感認為大概僅有半秒，於拍攝場景實際使用不會有大問題。拍攝時亦可以直接以 iPad 操控 iPhone 的各種設定，如果你需要一個人操作多部 iPhone 拍攝的話，這個功能相信非常適合你。</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/14/apple-vision-pro-preorder-2/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】Apple Vision Pro 香港預訂教學　戴眼鏡也能輕鬆買 + 臉部掃描過程</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/30/iphone-circle-to-search-by-shortcut/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】iPhone 也可「畫圈搜尋」　輕觸機背即可使用 + 即影即 Google</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/01/apple-starts-work-on-ios-19-and-macos-16/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">《彭博》指 Apple 已經著手開發，明年推出 iOS、macOS、watchOS 的新版本</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/30/final-cut-pro-4-iphone-camera/software/ipad-app/">【教學】Final Cut Pro 同時睇多部 iPhone 畫面　最多支援 4 部 + 延遲率低</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
